{"type": "article", "id": 28546, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-06-22T06:53:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 29265, "name": "Village Vanguard"}, {"id": 29266, "name": "Rice Creative"}, {"id": 24510, "name": "Marou"}, {"id": 29267, "name": "Buşra Tunç"}, {"id": 29268, "name": "Alissa Volchkova"}, {"id": 29168, "name": "北川大輔"}, {"id": 22011, "name": "ANDREA PONTI"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 25, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702153300gBfYlKHutRSMvPIz.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">          </p>\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h2>Lamalight by Buşra Tunç</h2>\n<p>来自伊斯坦布尔的建筑师和灯光艺术家 <a href=\"http://busratunc.com/\">Buşra Tunç</a> 和创意互动平台 <a href=\"http://atolyeistanbul.co/#atlye\">Atölye</a> 联手打造了一款可以适应各种室内设计的灯具 Lamalight。设计师的创作灵感来源于单条横线，弯管之间则采用了定制设计的 270 度可旋转不锈钢接头，可以展开成各种造型，在台灯、壁灯或者吊灯间转换，满足不同场合的需要。折叠型的设计使得它更便于包装和运输，看上去简约又紧凑。Lamalight 此前在米兰设计周上首次亮相，未来会在 Kickstarter 上展开众筹。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155539xm02Vpa4d8UyZkjO.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021555391FVQmZLsMXe6HlBI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021555416oiOFtIckDTvwsYg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155542C0Frd5ZbDPtuBxyn.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021555424r3Y52zwAQIoNPWd.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.41666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Liquid series by Alissa Volchkova</h2>\n<p>这个名为 Liquid 的瓷制容器系列是皇家艺术学院学生 <a href=\"http://www.alissavolchkova.com/\">Alissa Volchkova</a> 的毕业设计，将两大生产工艺汇集在了一起：先将陶泥塑造成形，然后浇上染色的釉料等待它自然干燥。通过这种随机的制作方式，最终的成品也具有了不可控性。每一件容器不仅实用，还可以创造出变化无穷的堆叠造型，将诗意的诠释与工业的概念结合在了一起。Liquid 系列计划于皇家艺术学院的 <a href=\"http://www.rca.ac.uk/news-and-events/events/show-rca-2016/\">showRCA 2016</a> 展上展出，展览日期为 6 月 26 日至 7 月 3 日。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155543ormjySC5pJneMwRi.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.77628362\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155544mXAR3f2zIwlCuBMr.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5391198\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155544S2Fv1UtEjMuwKHN7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.49022005\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155544IK5iRrFgnTJ6ewCl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155545H2NJbURCfpl3zVDg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155547y4YLamkSoOvxngdf.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55378973\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Corner by 北川大輔</h2>\n<p>如果你喜欢坐在角落的安全感，北川大輔设计的这款 <a href=\"http://www.designforindustry.jp/works/corner\">Corner</a> 座椅会是一个不错的选择。Corner 向两个方向打开，呈 L 字型，可以同时感受到被包围的安全感和开阔的宽敞感。上方的坐垫带给人一种柔软舒适的印象，与下方纤细扁平的金属椅腿形成了鲜明对比。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155547kmC50jrFEnVpRGUW.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155548ti8j20hfTW4RIScF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155548ulbqX5E0JIwTiN2G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155549uJiM6rVyCIKPjGH3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021555491KvnFmgUxR9qJ2VB.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155549SelB0yDEigoHqjYC.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>食パン座椅子 by Village Vanguard</h2>\n<p>想坐在松松软软的面包上？日本书屋 Village Vanguard 最近就推出了几款以面包为设计灵感的靠椅，除了普通的白面包和烤面包造型之外，还有打上鸡蛋的吐司款和发霉的面包款，松松软软的看上去特别可爱。包括平放在地上用作坐垫，靠椅共有五个倾斜角度能够满足不同的需要，外套也可以拆卸下来进行清洗。脑洞大开的书屋或许是考虑到人们夏天会宅在空调房间里，还额外设计了煎蛋造型的大毯子和护膝毯，可以说是种草能力一流。这是它的<a href=\"http://vvstore.jp/feature/detail/8309/\">预定链接</a>，座椅的价格从 5378 到 7538 日元不等。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155550CWFoIkGRnmarqfu9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021555504h9LkyTANG3rVsP6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155551GV7TJodLNWE0hwUH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155551ifCrAnORLEFVdelT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155552tR52qSnOhHdT6cPb.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021555530MhzwuZCBGv96amc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Ommo series by Andrea Ponti</h2>\n<p>还记得我们之前介绍过的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/26601.html\">鸭嘴兽茶滤</a>吗？如果你更喜欢简单的造型，不妨来看看 Andrea Ponti 设计的 Ommo 系列。甜甜圈造型的 Torus 挂在杯沿上就可以泡出一杯茶饮，平时也可以用来储存茶叶，多个 Torus 还可以叠在支架上。另一款茶滤 Koma 则有着圆形的底座和细长的把手，可以用来在冲泡时进行搅拌，上方的金属盖只需要轻轻一按就可以控制开阖。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155554uQ7oXidMtfVsrW20.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155554fY16ezpMuFXb3LN8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155555VpNhJMKrHgRLBU4C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155556H28UGBv1QXZ5RkOb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021555574F1AqDGNQRykfPT0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Marou chocolate by Rice Creative</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://rice-creative.com/\">Rice Creative</a> 最近接受了越南巧克力品牌 Marou 的委托，为其与新加坡国家美术馆（The National Gallery Singapore）的合作款设计了一套融合了美术馆建筑特色与越南传统版画工艺的包装。设计师们将美术馆三种不同的空间分别与巧克力的口味一一对应，设计出了三款图标。这些图标不仅出现在黑金配色的外壳左右两侧，还采用传统的 Đông Hồ 版画工艺由工匠手工印在桑皮纸包装上，过程中所使用到的染料均由当地的植物与贝壳制成。作为一款放在美术馆里销售的巧克力，包装本身就是一件承载了传统的艺术品。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155557BlkE03wfY9cUaPix.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155558V3uoBXAmkfISsJZD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155559dSv1OzqfmFy4RCZr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155559TE5suC10YWw9l2FS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155600S9Gzy2IBbMnKruZH.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155601pdXbrvuySVWm2FwT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}